<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes, rather than fire, primarily disturb stands of this alliance. However, the cespitose perennial nature of <i>Andropogon glomeratus, Schoenus nigricans</i> and related graminoids are likely to regenerate quickly after a fire.</div>
